---
const skills = [
  {
    label: 'Core',
    value: 'Backend development, data structures, cloud infrastructure, APIs, scaling and reliability',
  },
  {
    label: 'Languages',
    value: 'C#, Python, SQL / dbt, Node.js, C++, C, TypeScript, React, Flutter',
  },
  {
    label: 'Technologies',
    value: 'AWS (Certified), Docker, Airflow, CI / CD, Snowflake, Datadog, Terraform, Kubernetes',
  },
];
---

<section class="intro" id="intro" aria-labelledby="intro-lead">
  <div class="intro-inner">
    <div class="intro-main">
      <div class="intro-text">
        <h2 id="intro-lead" class="intro-lead">
          I build backend systems for financial workloads.
        </h2>

        <div class="intro-body">
          <p>
            Currently a senior software developer at Jasper Ridge Partners in Fort Worth, designing parallelized financial statement engines (one cut processing time by 80&ndash;90% over what it replaced), Bloomberg-integrated ETL pipelines, and accounting tooling for family-office portfolios. Mostly C#, dbt, and AWS, with the occasional React frontend when it's warranted.
          </p>
          <p>
            Before this: four years at Precocity (intern in 2019, promoted to full-time consultant after my MS), internships at Northrop Grumman patching security vulnerabilities in satellite software, and a BS/MS in Computer Engineering at Purdue. I'm drawn to the parts of a system that fall over at 3am: data reconciliation, parallelization, the recovery paths nobody wants to think about until they have to.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <figure class="intro-headshot">
        <img
          class="headshot-img"
          src="/images/headshot.png"
          alt="Aiden Gonzalez"
          width="4032"
          height="3024"
        />
      </figure>
    </div>

    <dl class="intro-skills">
      {skills.map((s) => (
        <>
          <dt class="skill-label label-mono">{s.label}</dt>
          <dd class="skill-value">{s.value}</dd>
        </>
      ))}
    </dl>
  </div>

  <footer class="intro-bottom">
    <p class="label-mono">keep going ↓</p>
  </footer>
</section>

<style>
  .intro {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-4) var(--space-10);
    box-sizing: border-box;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .intro {
      padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-12) var(--space-16);
    }
  }

  .intro-bottom,
  .intro-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width-wide);
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .intro-bottom {
    text-align: right;
  }

  .intro-bottom p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  /* The content area fills the space between top and bottom labels and centres vertically. */
  .intro-inner {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-10);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1100px) {
    .intro-inner {
      gap: var(--space-12);
    }
  }

  /* Two-column row: text on the left, headshot on the right.  Stacks on mobile (text first). */
  .intro-main {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-8);
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .intro-main {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.5fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: var(--space-12);
    }
  }

  .intro-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  /* Headshot column */
  .intro-headshot {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .headshot-img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 360px;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .intro-lead {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-2xl), 4.5vw, var(--text-3xl));
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 30ch;
  }

  .intro-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    max-width: var(--max-width-prose);
  }

  .intro-body p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .intro-skills {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: max-content minmax(0, 1fr);
    column-gap: var(--space-8);
    row-gap: var(--space-4);
    align-items: baseline;
    padding-top: var(--space-6);
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .skill-label {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .skill-value {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }
</style>
